<div id="assessment">
    <div {#if preview} {else}class="assessment-inner"{/if}>
        <section>
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="ol-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12 mx-auto">

                        <div class="card text-dark mb-2">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h1>{{title}}</h1>
                                <hr>
                                <div class="card mx-auto text-center">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <h4 class="card-title">UTech-SORAT</h4>
                                        <p class="card-text">
                                            UTECH SORAT (Student Online Readiness Assessment Tool) is a tool sponsored
                                            by The University of Technology, Office of Distance
                                            Learning (ODL). This tool assesses your online readiness and provides an
                                            analytical report
                                            in the form of a personal readiness profile highlighting areas of strengths
                                            and makes recommendations
                                            for improvement. UTECH SORAT in no way gives an absolute measure as to
                                            whether or not you
                                            are ready or will be successful in an online learning environment. This
                                            tool is intended
                                            to be used only as a guide. UTECH SORAT will also provide the Office of
                                            Distance Learning
                                            with statistical reports indicating the overall interest in online learning
                                            at the University
                                            of Technology, Jamaica.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <br>
                                <div class="progress" style="height: 20px">
                                    <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated progress-bar-gold"
                                        role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="100" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"
                                        style="width: 100%">100%</div>
                                </div>
                                <br>
                                <div class="text-center mb-2">
                                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-color">Show Results</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>